column2: We made it out. Let's all compare kills!
I need to rest my eyes.
We should hold and check for any diseases native to the medusozoa homeworld!
Let's eat smores around a campfire, guys!
This mission will earn me five commendations!
The night sky screams in agony...
Let's set up camp for now, people.
We're on a roll. Let's push through the night.
